PrecisAuthority to enter into a SUPPLEMENTARY AGREEMENT among the parties to the JOINT VENTURE AGREEMENT pertaining to the construction and operation of a bi-provincial heavy-oil upgrader at at Lloydminster, Saskatchewan, in order to provide for the making of additional financial contributions towards capital cost overruns.

precis:
Authority to enter into a SUPPLEMENTARY AGREEMENT among the parties to the
JOINT VENTURE AGREEMENT pertaining to the construction and operation of a
bi-provincial heavy-oil upgrader at at Lloydminster, Saskatchewan, in order
to provide for the making of additional financial contributions towards
capital cost overruns.
